  i386-win32
  x86_64-win64
  i386-wince
  arm-wince.

CPU_SOURCE is needed to build the 32bit version on 64bit systems.
Otherwise building svn2revisioninc crashes.
gtk2-64bit needs additional -FfApplicationServices
